                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf">Maṣḥafa qǝddāse</title>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="4r" to="6r"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1716Kidanz">ኪዳን፡ ዘነግህ፡</title>
                        <note>
                           The text follows a short invocation to Our Lady Mary: 
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡ እምነ፡ ወእሙ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ሰዓሊ፡ በእንቲአነ፡ ከመ፡ ይምሃረነ፡ ወይሣሃለነ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ወ</supplied>ያስተርኢ፡ ኂሩቱ፡ 
                              በላዕሌነ፡</q>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="6v" to="8v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4711Mastabqwe">መስተብቍዕ፡ ዘሐዋርያት፡</title>
                        <note>
                           Prayers for the sick, the pilgrims, the rain, the fruits of the earth, the water of the rivers, the king, the offerers, the sleepers, the catechumens, the peace.
                        </note>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           ናስተበቍዕ፡ ዘኵሎ፡ ይእኅዝ፡ እግዚአብ<supplied reason="omitted">ሔር</supplied>፡ አብ፡ ለእግዚእ<supplied reason="omitted">ነ</supplied>፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ 
                           ኢየሱስ፡ <choice>
                              <sic>ክርስትስ፡</sic>
                              <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ክርስቶስ፡</corr></choice>
                            እንዘ፡ 
                           
                              <sic>ነአኵት፡</sic>
                            በኵሉ፡ ወበውስተ፡ ኵሉ፡ እስመ፡ ከደነነ፡  
                              <sic>ወረደአነ፡</sic>
                            ሶቀነ፡ ወአብጽሐነ፡ እስከ፡ 
                           
                              <sic>ዘቲ፡</sic>
                            ሰዓት፡
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           እንዘ፡ ነሐዩ፡ በኵሉ፡ አምልኮ፡ ሠናይ፡ በፈሪሃ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወበኂ<add place="above">ሩ</add>ት፡ ንትረከብ፡ በክርስቶስ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                        </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                  
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
